{"tid":2386454,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"馬會會唔會比人告？（平機會）","createTime":"2021-01-29T14:44:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-31T04:24:15.000Z","uid":194318,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d55a91440c58a047c62636b19e1c98344db9652e","tid":2386454,"uid":194318,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:44:38.000Z","msg":"馬會而架只接受用投注戶口投注，好多癈老有得睇，無得賭，因為而架馬會開門都無開戶口服務。<br />\n咁耐不耐都會有人同d經理嘈，話去平機會告馬會，而經理既指示係令到d人向馬會投訴，落左啖氣就算，唔想驚動平機會。<br />\n我想研究下，其實馬會而架借疫情局人開投注戶口賭，又無引用政府任何指示，但唔比成年人就咁投注，係咪真係可以去平機會投訴？"},{"pid":"8ab28fd7e8cb510ad8a66746431b33ba5b696b41","tid":2386454,"uid":78243,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:51:10.000Z","msg":"馬會咪又係政府啲人﹐你估下佢會唔會告自己人"},{"pid":"c7d785551584b42c2522d08087ce480c0fd46341","tid":2386454,"uid":3522,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:52:37.000Z","msg":"平機會從來只告小市民"},{"pid":"f8ee3ec53a69fc3219f5ea2def72e1da90fab568","tid":2386454,"uid":227788,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T14:53:29.000Z","msg":"你以為<br />\n佢投注額節節上升<br />\n廢佬已經識用"},{"pid":"a2d1d499f7c5e203f43a680064d2a8f433d3b01e","tid":2386454,"uid":183844,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:04:46.000Z","msg":"入親馬會啲staff都會追過嚟sell你開ac<br />\n大條道理話啲廢老自己唔開啦<br />\n如果因為你哋唔開<br />\n我就直接覺得係你哋老人家唔識用<br />\n而唔係因為其他理由如鍾意揸住張飛咁去對嘅<br />\n又或者唔鐘意用電子嘢<br />\n咁呢個諗法我覺得更加係歧視喎"},{"pid":"5a22360c51aa20ca109207788bb24cfd02394796","tid":2386454,"uid":324681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:15:48.000Z","msg":"馬會有自動電話投注系統<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家其實經apps,上網同打電話都可以投注。"},{"pid":"b11e442ebc47ed8d5b2c3636ee1f23dbd3b3298b","tid":2386454,"uid":5220,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-29T15:18:10.000Z","msg":"要符合香港已立嘅反歧視法例先有得告架<br />\n唔係所有歧視都犯法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"752f44ca88ff638d1a2cdfb301270feb3cd3127f","tid":2386454,"uid":107590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T20:11:36.000Z","msg":"乜撚都投訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />on9香港人"},{"pid":"adc45db5cbb794ba0b1574309a855fe3c93c7e14","tid":2386454,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"大把廢老有戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識幾個50歲+ 的士佬，佢哋戶口既3條問題既答案，都係問題既最尾兩個字。<br />\n我懷疑係馬會啲人教佢地咁做。"},{"pid":"e8e42354789835b8762c68ce81feda3355aa471c","tid":2386454,"uid":32722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"adc45db5cbb794ba0b1574309a855fe3c93c7e14","tid":2386454,"uid":128210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-30T23:29:03.000Z","msg":"大把廢老有戶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n識幾個50歲+ 的士佬，佢哋戶口既3條問題既答案，都係問題既最尾兩個字。<br />\n我懷疑係馬會啲人教佢地咁做。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:22:51.000Z","msg":"笑到仆街"},{"pid":"ba20f0b8428c2fc73a81cf100e18973d2c5e3cb0","tid":2386454,"uid":352873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T04:24:15.000Z","msg":"馬會點解唔做埋放數？"}]}